<style>
  .glazur-about-page {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.35rem;
  }

  .glazur-about-page__gallery {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 0.85rem;
  }

  .glazur-about-page__photo {
    margin: 0;
    background: var(--color-surface, #fff);
    border: 1px solid rgba(74, 21, 54, 0.12);
  }

  .glazur-about-page__photo img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .glazur-about-page__copy p {
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    line-height: 1.62;
    color: var(--color-ink-muted, #5c4550);
  }

  .glazur-about-page__approach {
    margin-top: 1.35rem;
    padding-top: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(74, 21, 54, 0.12);
  }

  .glazur-about-page__approach h3 {
    margin: 0 0 0.7rem;
    font-family: var(--font-ui, Syne, sans-serif);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-plum, #4a1536);
  }

  .glazur-about-page__approach ul {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--color-ink-muted, #5c4550);
    line-height: 1.62;
  }

  .glazur-about-page__cta {
    margin-top: 1.2rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .glazur-about-page__gallery {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>

{%- assign about_photo_1 = settings.about_photo_1 -%}
{%- assign about_photo_2 = settings.about_photo_2 -%}

<div class="glazur-about-page">
  <div class="glazur-about-page__gallery" aria-label="Glazur founder photos">
    <figure class="glazur-about-page__photo">
      {% if about_photo_1 != blank %}
        {% assign about_photo_1_alt = about_photo_1.alt | default: 'Glazur portrait in Paris' %}
        {{
          about_photo_1
          | image_url: width: 1200
          | image_tag: alt: about_photo_1_alt, loading: 'lazy', decoding: 'async'
        }}
      {% else %}
        <img
          src="{{ 'glazur-about-photo-1.png' | asset_url }}"
          width="995"
          height="1003"
          alt="Glazur portrait in Paris"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
        >
      {% endif %}
    </figure>
    <figure class="glazur-about-page__photo">
      {% if about_photo_2 != blank %}
        {% assign about_photo_2_alt = about_photo_2.alt | default: 'Glazur style look in city' %}
        {{
          about_photo_2
          | image_url: width: 1200
          | image_tag: alt: about_photo_2_alt, loading: 'lazy', decoding: 'async'
        }}
      {% else %}
        <img
          src="{{ 'glazur-about-photo-2.png' | asset_url }}"
          width="666"
          height="888"
          alt="Glazur style look in city"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
        >
      {% endif %}
    </figure>
  </div>

  <div class="glazur-about-page__copy">
    <p>
      Glazur is a brand for women who believe that everyday life can be beautiful. We create clothing that transforms
      ordinary days into small moments of magic: soft fabrics, thoughtful fit, and refined details make a woman feel
      confident, graceful, and inspired.
    </p>
    <p>
      Our pieces are designed in Paris and crafted with careful attention to every detail. We release limited editions,
      where each item is unique and features a signature touch - a Glazur Detail, a small element that makes the look
      truly special.
    </p>
    <p>
      We use only natural fabrics - cotton and linen - because we believe in beauty you can touch and feel. Lace,
      embroidery, delicate bows, and fine finishes create a sense of quiet luxury and gentle transformation: from tired
      and busy to inspired and graceful.
    </p>
    <p>
      Glazur is not about an outfit, it is a state of being. Every day in our clothing feels more beautiful, and the
      subtle admiration of those around you confirms it: you stand out gracefully, feminine, and uniquely. This is for
      women who want to feel exceptional, here and now.
    </p>

    <div class="glazur-about-page__approach">
      <h3>Our approach</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Limited drops designed in Paris and crafted with attention to detail.</li>
        <li>Natural fabrics with tactile finishes for everyday elegance.</li>
        <li>Signature Glazur Details that make each piece feel personal.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="glazur-about-page__cta">
      <a class="btn btn--fill" href="{% render 'glazur-collection-url', key: 'default' %}">Go to catalog</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
